**Description:** **: This script is an interactive command-line interface (CLI) tool designed for processing text files using the X.AI API. It allows users to input a file path, reads a preview of the file content, and uses the X.AI API to generate a detailed description of the content, identify its type and key topics, and suggest a new descriptive filename. The script handles errors, logs activities, and includes options to rename files based on the API's suggestions. It also saves metadata from the API response to a JSON file.

